<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٠٥٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5093">أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6092">مِسْعَرٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2287">سَعْدٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3708">ابْنِ شَدَّادٍ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4500">عَلِيًّا </a><span class="special">﵁</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«مَا سَمِعْتُ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَجْمَعُ أَبَوَيْهِ لِأَحَدٍ غَيْرَِ سَعْدٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>